{"about_the_game":"<br><br>[Retail Company Simulator: Prologue is a free prologue version of Retail Company Simulator. In this game, you'll have a limited amount of contracts.]<br><br>This is a first-person simulation game where you run a retail company.<br>Expand your humble store into a huge retail company.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/Store01_3.gif?t=1727342465\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Store Workflow</h2>Sign contracts with leading brands, order new products with an in-game computer, unpack the boxes, place the products into your store, and set the prices for your products.<br>Consider the market prices while setting up your product prices in the store for customer satisfaction.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/Contract01.gif?t=1727342465\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Products</h2>Please make sure your customers find all their needs in the store.<br>Always expand your product portfolio and satisfy your customers.<br>Shirts, jackets, pants, sweatshirts, dresses, t-shirts, shoes, hats, and more...<br>Be aware of the market prices and purchase more products when they're cheap.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/ShelfFill03_1.gif?t=1727342465\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customers</h2>Place a sufficient number of checkouts and fitting rooms to reduce the waiting time for customers.<br>Scan products and collect payments whether in cash or with card purchases.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/Checkout01_1.gif?t=1727342465\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Expansions and New Teammates</h2>Expand your store and warehouse by leveling up your store and budget.<br>Hire stockers to fill the racks.<br>Purchase more cash registers and hire new cashiers to minimiz